Rules:
- Entities must be grounded in the chunk. Do not invent entities the text does not name.
- Relationships must connect entities you listed. Do not reference external entities.
- Prefer fewer, higher-quality entities over many trivial ones. Target 3–10 per chunk for substantive text.
